channel.title: A new RSPS Into life?
channel.description:
Hello, I've been wanting to make a good RSPS server for a long time now and I need someone who is a good coder and knows a bit of RS. I've got the server all sorted so don't worry about paying anything. All We need is a client/server source to get going and setup a website etc. If you want to help add me on skype: TheCharlieHD
Thanks in advance.
